p: As indicated in Table 1, 13 compounds were identified in the oil. The main constituents of the oil were 1,8-cineole (41.2 ± 1.3%), linalool acetate (11.0 ± 0.5%), and α-terpinyl acetate (6.0 ± 0.4%). The percentage of monoterpene hydrocarbons (72.3%) was higher than sesquiterpene hydrocarbons (7.3%).
